      "span_text": "Chemical analysis of river sand in our previous research [CITATION_1] showed that the main component of sand was SiO 2 , and the content of iron, aluminum and calcium, those elements that were related with P precipitation, were 9.10g/kg, 14.77 g/kg and 0.14 g/kg, respectively."
